<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/accounts-payable/accounts-payable-invoice-matching.md" sourcestartlinenumber="127">The net unit price tolerance for the USB Drive item is 10%.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/accounts-payable/accounts-payable-invoice-matching.md" sourcestartlinenumber="128">The price totals matching tolerance for the legal entity is 15% or 500.00.</li>
</ul>
